subject: Television
Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Twenty-one Nascar Sunday afternoon races, including the Daytona 500, will start at 1 p.m. Eastern. All Saturday night races will begin at 7:30 p.m.
